            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
